name: ChronicKidneyDisease
title: Chronic Kidney Disease
description: This value set is created for MSSP ACO-38 Risk-Standardized Acute Admission Rates for Patients with Multiple Chronic Conditions measure and represents the chronic condition of Chronic Kidney Disease (CKD).
purpose: (Clinical Focus: The chronic condition of Chronic Kidney Disease (CKD).),(Data Element Scope: Condition, Claim Diagnosis),(Inclusion Criteria: ICD10CM codes for the chronic condition of Chronic Kidney Disease (CKD).),(Exclusion Criteria: n/a)
